                <h2>Headers</h2>
                <p>Winstrap headers are responsive. By default, <code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> to <code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> are mapped to Winstrap header controls.</p>
                <p>You can also apply headers using the Sass mixin. Headers applied using the mixin are not responsive by default. Pass the <code>responsive</code> argument to make them responsive.</p>
            </div>
